original_title: Lara Croft XXX: A Harry Sparks Parody
overview: Archeologist, Lara Croft, and her best friend, Samantha, embark on a quest to find a lost treasure on a mysterious island. But soon they discover there is more there than they expected. Starring Val Dodds as Lara Croft and Jenna Sativa as Samantha.
title: Lara Croft XXX: A Harry Sparks Parody
